Package demoworld.model

Class Stat

Object
Stat
All Implemented Interfaces:
Named
Direct Known Subclasses:
Hitpoints, PrimaryStat
public class Stat extends Object implements Named
Representation of some Named statistic (Stat) of a Character, an object constructed from multiple Values with a name and a description.

  • Constructor Details

    • Stat

      public Stat(String name, String description, int min, int max, int current)
      Constructs a Stat.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the new Stat
      description - the description of the new Stat
      min - initial minimum of both the base Value and the modifier Value in the new Stat
      max - initial maximum of both the base Value and the modifier Value in the new Stat
      current - initial current of the base Value in the new Stat (the current of the modifier Value is always initialised to zero, i.e. not modified)
